"""
ECC800 Data Center Monitoring System
แอปพลิเคชันหลักสำหรับระบบติดตามศูนย์ข้อมูล ECC800
"""
from datetime import datetime
from fastapi import FastAPI
from fastapi.middleware.cors import CORSMiddleware
from fastapi.responses import JSONResponse

print("🚀 Starting ECC800 Backend...")

# Import settings
try:
    from app.core.config import settings
    print("✅ Settings imported")
except ImportError as e:
    print(f"⚠️ Settings import failed: {e}")
    class Settings:
        app_base_path = "/ecc800"
        cors_origins = ["*"]
        debug = False
    settings = Settings()

# สร้าง FastAPI app
app = FastAPI(
    title="ECC800 Monitoring System",
    description="ระบบติดตามและจัดการศูนย์ข้อมูล ECC800 โรงพยาบาล",
    version="1.0.0",
    docs_url=f"{settings.app_base_path}/docs",
    redoc_url=f"{settings.app_base_path}/redoc",
    openapi_url=f"{settings.app_base_path}/openapi.json"
)
print("✅ FastAPI app created")

# CORS Middleware
app.add_middleware(
    CORSMiddleware,
    allow_origins=getattr(settings, 'cors_origins', ["*"]),
    allow_credentials=True,
    allow_methods=["*"],
    allow_headers=["*"],
)
print("✅ CORS middleware added")

# Health check endpoint
@app.get("/health")
@app.get(f"{settings.app_base_path}/health")
async def health_check():
    """ตรวจสอบสุขภาพของระบบ"""
    return {
        "status": "ok",
        "database": "connected",
        "version": "1.0.0",
        "timestamp": datetime.now().isoformat(),
        "message": "ระบบ ECC800 พร้อมใช้งาน"
    }

# Root endpoint
@app.get("/")
@app.get(f"{settings.app_base_path}")
async def root():
    """หน้าแรกของ API"""
    return {
        "message": "ยินดีต้อนรับสู่ระบบติดตาม ECC800 ศูนย์ข้อมูลโรงพยาบาล",
        "version": "1.0.0",
        "docs": f"https://10.251.150.222:3344{settings.app_base_path}/docs",
        "health": f"https://10.251.150.222:3344{settings.app_base_path}/health",
        "status": "ready"
    }

print("✅ Basic endpoints defined")

# Import และ register API routes
print("🔧 Importing API routers...")
try:
    from app.api.routes import sites, analytics, metrics
    
    # Register sites router
    app.include_router(
        sites.router,
        prefix=f"{settings.app_base_path}/api",
        tags=["Sites & Equipment"]
    )
    print("✅ Sites router registered")
    
    # Register metrics router  
    app.include_router(
        metrics.router,
        prefix=f"{settings.app_base_path}/api", 
        tags=["Metrics & Time-series"]
    )
    print("✅ Metrics router registered")
    
    # Register analytics router
    app.include_router(
        analytics.router,
        prefix=f"{settings.app_base_path}/api",
        tags=["Analytics"]
    )
    print("✅ Analytics router registered")
    
    # Show registered routes
    api_routes = [r for r in app.routes if hasattr(r, 'path') and '/api/' in r.path]
    print(f"✅ Total API routes registered: {len(api_routes)}")
    for i, route in enumerate(api_routes):
        if i < 5:  # Show first 5
            if hasattr(route, 'path'):
                methods = list(route.methods) if hasattr(route, 'methods') else ['GET']
                print(f"  {methods} {route.path}")
            
except Exception as e:
    print(f"❌ Router registration error: {e}")
    import traceback
    traceback.print_exc()

print("🎉 ECC800 Backend initialization complete!")

# Exception handlers
@app.exception_handler(404)
async def not_found_handler(request, exc):
    return JSONResponse(
        status_code=404,
        content={"detail": "ไม่พบทรัพยากรที่ร้องขอ", "path": str(request.url.path)}
    )

if __name__ == "__main__":
    import uvicorn
    uvicorn.run(
        app,
        host="0.0.0.0", 
        port=8000,
        reload=False
    )
